TI  - An oral pH-activated "nano-bomb" carrier combined with berberine by regulating gene silencing and gut microbiota for site-specific treatment of ulcerative colitis
T2  - BIOMATERIALS SCIENCE
LA  - English
KW  - INFLAMMATORY-BOWEL-DISEASE
KW  - INTESTINAL HOMEOSTASIS
