TI  - Nanoparticle curcumin ameliorates experimental colitis via modulation of gut microbiota and induction of regulatory T cells (Publication with Expression of Concern)
T2  - PLOS ONE
LA  - English
KW  - INFLAMMATORY-BOWEL-DISEASE
KW  - NF-KAPPA-B
KW  - ULCERATIVE-COLITIS
KW  - CONTROLLED-TRIAL
