TI  - Protein-based micro- and nano-transporters for gut microbiota modulators: advances in delivery strategies and gut health benefits
T2  - FRONTIERS IN BIOENGINEERING AND BIOTECHNOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - gut microbiota
KW  - gut disorders
KW  - probiotics
KW  - bioactive phytochemicals
