TI  - Icariside II ameliorates slow transit constipation by inhibiting macrophage polarization and suppressing the cGAS-STING pathway
T2  - EUROPEAN JOURNAL OF PHARMACOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Slow transit constipation
KW  - Icariside II
